caption.p: SFE suppressed the growth of H1299 human lung cancer cells and HCT116 human colon cancer cells. H1299 (a) and HCT116 cells (b) were treated with SFE (0–1,000 μg/ml) for 24 hr, 48 hr, and 72 hr, and viable cells were shown as % of control. Different letters (a‐g) indicate significance ( p < .05)
